headline: Pentair (PNR) Q2 Earnings Preview: What You Should Know Beyond the Headline Estimates
summary: Evaluate the expected performance of Pentair (PNR) for the quarter ended June 2025, looking beyond the conventional Wall Street top-and-bottom-line estimates and examining some of its key metrics for better insight.
